Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming up, huh?\N The competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get spooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it....\Ndon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you get humiliated,\Nor if they all laugh at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're going to abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're not Beethoven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, you're\Nnot Chopin, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Are you ready\Nto go on your journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cover him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes from the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.51,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daito Middle\N\NSumiya Middle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That whistle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...reflecting irregularly\Nacross the clear skies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Watari ended up losing, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cry. We gave it\Nour best shot, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we gotta go shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for rooting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I missed my chance at becoming\Na star. So the rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play again in high school, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you were cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll have to wait till high\Nschool to become a star, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit! No way am I\Ngonna lose next time, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari and Tsubaki... their last junior\Nhigh tournaments have ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.99,Maihou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maihou Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm at the point where I can\Nplay my selection by heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima! We're in class here! Dial it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three more laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari and Tsubaki both\Nsparkled. And so did you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were there... so commanding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I have a deep understanding?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I made Chopin my own?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somewhere in this music\N that follows these notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...do I exist?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly are you in all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody get him some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go get the nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friend A!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.49,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Munch Munch*
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeeees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skipping meals... passing out!\NYour body is an important asset!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do? I\Nwas totally immersed, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt better after I ate the egg\Nsandwiches Tsubaki gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five packs of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? There's\Na park over there, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She would eat my candy\Nwhenever I wasn't looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I named her Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was fooling around with Chelsea like\Nalways. I guess I was over-attentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One day, she scratched my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My hand was bright red. The blood was\Ngushing, and wouldn't stop... I panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, my mother took her\Nsomewhere and abandoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The scars Chelsea left me\Nremind me of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew one of my few memories\Nwould be something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just stared at my mother's back\Nwithout a word as she took Chelsea away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Stop it!" or "Wait a minute..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd say something like that,\N things might have been different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, I've been in my mom's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like egg sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You also like Moo Moo Brand milk.\NUnexpectedly, you have a sweet tooth, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not good at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for Tsubaki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you're a little bit jealous of\Nthat chick-magnet, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in your\Nmother's shadow at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're you. "To be like you..." -\Nit's not so ambiguous as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, no matter how\Nyou change, it doesn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I weren't born in Europe,\Nand we don't have weird haircuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're not Chopin, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just play with sincerity, give the performance\Nof your life with everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really have a way with words sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Sometimes?\NListen, I'm encouraging you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With sincerity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"When you're depressed, it always\Nhelps to lean your head on your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arms like to feel useful."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are big, knobby hands.\NThey're the hands of a pianist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are happy to be touching mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're beside themselves,\Nitching to play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After struggling, losing my way, and suffering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer I arrived at was so laughably simple...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So-so, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The competition's tomorrow, right?\N You still can't hear the notes, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But see, there's this girl, and she\Nseriously believes in the power of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I'll try believing in it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that person will come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should take it easy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's going to be a big day for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The list of contestants?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your entry number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Köchel number 265, Mozart's\NTwinkle, Twinkle, Little Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stars will shine over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stars in broad daylight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An encounter with my past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My competition begins now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.31,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Competition Finalists
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it! My name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I thought I was in the zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was your son, Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My child didn't qualify again. I feel\Nbitter, but they were outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emi Igawa and Takeshi Aiza...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were head and shoulders above the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer amount of practice\Nthey've put in is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was the fruit of all those lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it all the more disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.49,SSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima\N\N\N\NEmi Igawa\N\N\N\NTakeshi Aiza
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it makes Arima-kun\Nlook that much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they served as Arima-kun's foils yet again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really pisses me off, that Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we lost to him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just setting the\Nstage to win the final.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But aside from that... That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He went home without even looking at\N the results, like he just assumed he'd won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, would it kill him\Nto look the least bit happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That in itself pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not interested. Not in\Nother people, and not in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably... not in himself, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are cool about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never been\Nhumiliated like this before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he has no interest in us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm gonna force him with\Nall my might to look our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him care.\NSomeday... I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to destroy you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He looks a little more grown\Nup. But he hasn't changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those annoying black-rimmed\Nglasses are the same. Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a lot of people here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a preliminary round,\Nthis is a pretty big turnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It could be the Arima-kun Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, in the restroom, all\Neverybody could talk about was Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really big deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so smug, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But listen, this vibe\NI'm getting is kinda weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to show off his\Nmind-blowing technique again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly as the score's written,\Ntotally under his mother's thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the secret marionette playing method!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do people hate Kousei or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To follow the score, and to play\Nexactly as the composer intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's an incredible feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a competition, they can\Nonly judge you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but he can actually win just\Nby being faithful to the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He can actually raise the bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what doesn't sit well with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the younger generation,\Nwho seek out something from music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, there's jealousy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Arima-kun did storm his\Nway through all those competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There was a time when\Nhe entered a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it was around the time\Nhis mother was hospitalized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a digital watch, never off by\Neven a split second... Nothing resonates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Human Metronome. Made of concrete.\NHis mother's puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A slave to the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The name "Kousei Arima" is infamous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Bring it on! Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that? I'm gonna kick his butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Arima, he's totally forgotten us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have an early start time, right?\NGo get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And besides, it's not like Arima forgot us.\NHe never knew us from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's exactly the same as\Nhe was two years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't like him. Just because his mother\Nas a famous instructor's student,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he got all that special treatment...\NBut for someone with all those skills,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he never plays anything\Nbut boring music!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Judging will now commence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met him was in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time, for sure... next time, for sure..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And just when I thought I had him,\Nafter stretching out my arms all the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a mirage, he faded into the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was like the dove in a magic\Ntrick - poof, he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, finally, he's returned to where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this day for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At last...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The competition is\Nabout to begin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate judging because\Nit's so exhausting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again? He's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. 3, Miss Yuko Kawanaka,\Nplease get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna be all right.\NYou can do this. You can play it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is weird... Is it\Nbecause it's been two years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never gone through this before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a broken see-saw, my\Nheart's pounding like crazy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did he forget how to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's one less competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared, I'm scared, I'm scared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared, I'm scared, I'm scared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza-kun, please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared, I'm scared, I'm scared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all afraid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To get up onstage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe you'll mess up. Maybe\Nthey'll totally reject you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so... You grit your teeth\Nand get up onstage anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me... or is there a\Ndifferent vibe in here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The overwhelming favorite\Nto win just took the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last year's champion, Takeshi Aiza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is. Now I can finally\Nlisten to the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chopin, Étude Op. 10, No. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like your expression.\NDon't get overeager, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be going to Germany.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enter the\NMaihou Music Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they invited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a golden opportunity to get overseas\Nexposure before the Chopin competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already won Maihou last year,\Nso there's no reason to make it a priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadows Whisper
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:38.94,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8\NResound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:55.00,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
